name: ExtensionStructureMap_Group_Rule
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.StructureMap.group.rule` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `StructureMap.group.rule` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `StructureMap.group.rule` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`StructureMap.group.rule` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `StructureMap.group.rule` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `StructureMap.group.rule` 1..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `StructureMap.group.rule` 1..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `StructureMap.group.rule` is mapped to FHIR R4 element `StructureMap.group.rule`.
